snippet.title: Amanda Mc.
snippet.description:
Registered Nurse with Rheumatoid Arthritis, seeking to spread awareness about overall health and wellness. I am also passionate about exposing MLM businesses that manipulate and target those who are vulnerable, and/or naive, all to make the rich richer and the poor poorer, especially as it pertains to the health and wellness industry.
(I recommend playing my videos in 1.25x speed or faster if longer videos aren't your jam ;-) )
